</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="29" pageNumber="757" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="29.[1371,2577,1057,1760]" pageId="29" pageNumber="757">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1371,1608,1450,1483]" pageId="29" pageNumber="757">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
There is no specific information available for this species, but, the Borneo Black-banded Squirrel is diurnal.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
