</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="29" pageNumber="757" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="29.[1371,2577,1057,1760]" pageId="29" pageNumber="757">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1373,1724,1608,1641]" pageId="29" pageNumber="757">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. The Borneo Black-banded Squirrel has a wide distribution and appears to have a stable population. Some forestloss is occurring throughoutits distribution.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
